advisor.user:
Student: {student}
Scores: pre {pre_score_text}, post {post_score_text}, change {score_delta_text}
Test performance summary:
{test_report}
Dimension scores: {score_overview}
Weak points:
{weak_points}
Evaluation JSON:
{evaluation_json}

Output JSON:
- general_advice.summary: overall advice, highlight strengths and next focus;
- general_advice.recommended_resources: 1-2 key readings/guidelines/cases or practice directions most relevant to this case;
- detailed_advice: array, up to 3 items. Each has dimension (use English titles above), issue, suggestion. Keep issue/suggestion concise and actionable.
